A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Environment – Building Energy Performance Standards – Repeal
3 FOR the purpose of repealing certain provisions of law establishing and governing building
4 energy performance standards; and generally relating to building energy
5 performance standards.
